data.description: Nestled in a prime locale, this 3-bed, 2-bath residence is the epitome of comfortable living. The fenced backyard, ideal for family moments, opens to a spacious deck--perfect for gatherings. The expansive master bedroom features a walk-in closet, while generous storage graces the spare bedrooms. A reliable 10-year-old roof adds value and peace of mind. Enjoy seamless connectivity with Co-Mo Connect for high-speed internet. Your dream home awaits, offering both practicality and charm. Make cherished memories in this inviting abode!
